sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as App Mobile/Web
    participant API as API (/api/novo/users/signup)
    participant BA as Better-Auth Service
    participant DB as Banco de Dados (Prisma)

    App->>API: POST { name, email, password, cpf, phone... }
    API->>DB: Verifica duplicidade (Email/CPF)
    Note over DB: Se existir, retorna 400
    API->>BA: auth.api.signUpEmail({ email, password, name })
    BA->>DB: Cria registro na tabela 'user' (Status: PENDING)
    BA->>DB: Hook After: Cria PatientProfile vazio
    BA-->>API: Retorna objeto 'createdUser'
    API->>DB: prisma.patientProfile.upsert (Atualiza CPF/Phone/BirthDate)
    API-->>App: 201 Created ("Aguardando aprovação")
